### Week 4 Reality Check

**We fall short by $32,500.**

**Why?**
1. Conversion rates are optimistic (30-40% assumes HOT leads)
2. Enterprise deals take longer than 7-14 days in reality
3. No existing pipeline to start from
4. Decision-makers on vacation, internal approvals, payment delays

**What would it take to hit $100K?**
- Need 11 enterprise deals total (not 5) = $110K
- OR 17 growth + 3 enterprise = $100K
- OR 40 growth + 20 starter = $90K (still short)

**The math only works if:**
- You have 20+ hot leads TODAY
- 50%+ close rate (requires known personal brand / warm referrals)
- Same-day contract + payment turnaround

**Revised moderate target: $60-75K in 25 days** (still aggressive but possible)

